{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"传家宝","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":11,"day":18}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈阳部队某部九连演唱组集体创"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:勤俭是传家宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们要记牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝缝补补咱们都来学。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:艰苦朴素的老传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:咱们要继承好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:哎叫声同志们:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:细听我们谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:我家住谦德庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:哎我住北大关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:我住南门西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁:哎我住鼓楼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:我们都是天津兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入伍在同一年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:来到部队两年多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:一直在九连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:艰苦朴素的好作风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:全都有锻炼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:哎咱就说说我吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家住在天津卫，就有十几年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从小在学校，一直把书念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:学生!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在家又是老疙瘩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父母把我惯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣服脏了不会洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破了不会连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前年来当兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就来到咱们连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:对!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗缝补衣服是我的难关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就说这白衬衣吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿上懒得换，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脏得实在没办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就脱了扔一边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:好嘛!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老同志给我洗了无数件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经常让别人洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在太丢脸啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:哎你自己也得要好好来锻炼!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:哎是得好好练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次，洗衣服，一点没经验。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:头一回!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大堆的脏衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放在盆里边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打来了开水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我猛往盆里灌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泡了足有两钟头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才动手干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:干了!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出刚要洗呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可就傻了眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:泡好你就洗么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为嘛傻了眼哪?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:你往盆里着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿军装，红线衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有白衬衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泡的时间长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颜色全都变了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:嗬!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的沾上了绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的染上了蓝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这漂漂亮亮的白衬衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就成了花衬衫啦!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:好嘛!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里虽然急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还得动手干哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打上肥皂，我猛搓好几遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个小时后，我总算给洗完了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再往上看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一件白衬衣就根本没法穿了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:哎?!才刚洗过的白衬衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为嘛不能穿!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:我用的劲头大，把布搓开绽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油泥一点没洗掉，窟窿连成片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这件衣服象鱼网，叫我怎么穿?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:不能穿。)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:你先别着急呀，也别怕困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万事就怕有心人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以后你慢慢练!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:对!功夫到自然成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难事就怕练!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:通过这件事，深深教育了咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我下定决心好好来锻炼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你再看现在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和以前不一般，洗缝补衣服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我样样都学全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再有针线活，根本没困难了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁:哎你先少说点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再听我来谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在家对缝补也是不习惯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尤其从思想，对它就讨厌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那阵总寻思呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们都是老爷们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堂堂的男子汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘腿揑脚的针线活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干着不体面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣服破了我不管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全由妈妈干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到连队后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就为了难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这洗缝补衣服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全得自己干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎就说这床被吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我准备盖到完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是不拆也不洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直到复员了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:这样可不行啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁早快点干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脏了不洗不卫生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也实在太难看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:对!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁:你说的是实情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我不敢干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怕的是拆完后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给自己找为难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在没办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只好硬着干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拆完我就洗呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千了我就连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:干啦!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这每一针每一线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都比刺杀难!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:嗬!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就说这根针吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也故意要笑咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是调皮捣蛋不听咱使唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎的我这手啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象蝎子整一般，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:疼啊!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我咬着牙耐着疼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憋得直冒汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早晨，到中午，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整整是半天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这床要命的被子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我总算给缝完啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:不容易!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里很高兴啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上带笑颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心想自己能做被子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可真是不简单。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我准备来叠好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放在床头前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我刚一拿呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这被子底下就带了一大串!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:哎这是怎么回事?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快对我们谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁:我急忙来现看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:怎么样?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是把褥子和床单一起都缝连!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:嗬!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又是气又是笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是太丢脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:这时候，老班长走到他跟前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面上微微笑，一劲拍他肩:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:你别着急别灰心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是缺锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来帮你忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拆了咱重干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁:说完后，老班长他就动手干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不大会功夫，被子全做完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再往上看，(怎么样)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长的针线活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做的真美观。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我越看越纳闷，上前开了言:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长你是男同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎会做针线哪?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:班长做完后，笑着开了言:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙:我咋到连队，也不会缝连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每逢遇到针线活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己总为难，咱们老首长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耐心教给咱。这不光是缝补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想也锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它锻炼咱们不忘本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克勤又克俭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:对!咱们的老班长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年复了员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲:临走之前跟我把话谈:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:说的嘛?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要忘记了，你长在红军连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们连的光荣传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要牢牢记心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(合:对!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他顺手拿出针线包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"递到我跟前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是咱们的传家宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装的是针和线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让这每一针每一线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和红军紧相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:小小针线包，意义不平凡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从建军，到现在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传了多少年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙:用它来补衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比那盔甲坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级的糖衣炮弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是打不穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级革命本色永远不会变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁:哎用它补袜子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"补绽把脚垫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它能使你站得稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命意志坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级的香风臭气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把咱吹不翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要当好红色接班人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接好革命班!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合:接过传家宝，立即发誓言:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级纯朴作风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代代往下传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级的坏思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要连根一齐铲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习雷锋，学习好八连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远革命，永不变质，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远奔向前!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(战士业余演出队节目选)"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}